query_sql_text: SELECT s.SALE_ID, s.AMOUNT, s.QUANTITY, c.CUSTOMER_NAME, d.DATE_FULL FROM fact.FACT_SALES s INNER JOIN dim.DIM_CUSTOMER c ON s.CUSTOMER_KEY = c.CUSTOMER_KEY INNER JOIN dim.DIM_DATE d ON s.DATE_KEY = d.DATE_KEY WHERE s.AMOUNT > 1000 AND d.YEAR = 2024

query_sql_text: SELECT SUM(s.AMOUNT) as TOTAL_SALES, AVG(s.AMOUNT) as AVG_SALE, COUNT(*) as SALE_COUNT FROM fact.FACT_SALES s INNER JOIN dim.DIM_DATE d ON s.DATE_KEY = d.DATE_KEY WHERE d.YEAR = 2024 AND d.MONTH >= 1 AND d.MONTH <= 3 GROUP BY d.MONTH ORDER BY d.MONTH
SELECT c.CUSTOMER_KEY, c.CUSTOMER_NAME, c.EMAIL, c.CITY, c.STATE FROM dim.DIM_CUSTOMER c WHERE c.STATE = 'CA' AND c.ACTIVE_FLAG = 1

query_sql_text: SELECT d.DATE_KEY, d.DATE_FULL, d.YEAR, d.MONTH, d.DAY, d.QUARTER FROM dim.DIM_DATE d WHERE d.DATE_FULL BETWEEN '2024-01-01' AND '2024-12-31' ORDER BY d.DATE_FULL

query_sql_text: SELECT s.PRODUCT_KEY, p.PRODUCT_NAME, SUM(s.QUANTITY) as TOTAL_QTY, SUM(s.AMOUNT) as TOTAL_AMOUNT, COUNT(DISTINCT s.CUSTOMER_KEY) as UNIQUE_CUSTOMERS FROM fact.FACT_SALES s INNER JOIN dim.DIM_PRODUCT p ON s.PRODUCT_KEY = p.PRODUCT_KEY WHERE s.AMOUNT > 500 GROUP BY s.PRODUCT_KEY, p.PRODUCT_NAME HAVING SUM(s.AMOUNT) > 10000 ORDER BY TOTAL_AMOUNT DESC

SELECT TOP 100 s.SALE_ID, s.AMOUNT, s.SALE_DATE, c.CUSTOMER_NAME FROM fact.FACT_SALES s INNER JOIN dim.DIM_CUSTOMER c ON s.CUSTOMER_KEY = c.CUSTOMER_KEY WHERE s.SALE_DATE >= DATEADD(day, -30, GETDATE()) ORDER BY s.AMOUNT DESC
SELECT COUNT(*) as RECORD_COUNT FROM fact.FACT_SALES WHERE SALE_DATE >= '2024-01-01'

SELECT p.CATEGORY, p.SUBCATEGORY, COUNT(DISTINCT p.PRODUCT_KEY) as PRODUCT_COUNT, AVG(s.AMOUNT) as AVG_SALE_AMOUNT FROM dim.DIM_PRODUCT p LEFT JOIN fact.FACT_SALES s ON p.PRODUCT_KEY = s.PRODUCT_KEY GROUP BY p.CATEGORY, p.SUBCATEGORY ORDER BY PRODUCT_COUNT DESC

query_sql_text: SELECT d.YEAR, d.QUARTER, SUM(s.AMOUNT) as QUARTERLY_SALES, AVG(s.AMOUNT) as AVG_SALE, MAX(s.AMOUNT) as MAX_SALE, MIN(s.AMOUNT) as MIN_SALE, STDEV(s.AMOUNT) as STDEV_SALE FROM fact.FACT_SALES s INNER JOIN dim.DIM_DATE d ON s.DATE_KEY = d.DATE_KEY GROUP BY d.YEAR, d.QUARTER ORDER BY d.YEAR, d.QUARTER

SELECT c.CUSTOMER_KEY, c.CUSTOMER_NAME, COUNT(s.SALE_ID) as ORDER_COUNT, SUM(s.AMOUNT) as LIFETIME_VALUE FROM dim.DIM_CUSTOMER c INNER JOIN fact.FACT_SALES s ON c.CUSTOMER_KEY = s.CUSTOMER_KEY WHERE c.ACTIVE_FLAG = 1 GROUP BY c.CUSTOMER_KEY, c.CUSTOMER_NAME HAVING COUNT(s.SALE_ID) >= 5 ORDER BY LIFETIME_VALUE DESC

query_sql_text: SELECT s.STORE_KEY, s.STORE_NAME, s.REGION, COUNT(DISTINCT sal.CUSTOMER_KEY) as UNIQUE_CUSTOMERS FROM dim.DIM_STORE s INNER JOIN fact.FACT_SALES sal ON s.STORE_KEY = sal.STORE_KEY WHERE s.ACTIVE_FLAG = 1 GROUP BY s.STORE_KEY, s.STORE_NAME, s.REGION

query_sql_text: SELECT c.CITY, c.STATE, COUNT(*) as CUSTOMER_COUNT FROM dim.DIM_CUSTOMER c WHERE c.EMAIL LIKE '%@gmail.com' GROUP BY c.CITY, c.STATE ORDER BY CUSTOMER_COUNT DESC
